data.description: Welcome to Your Dream Home in Holly Ridge, NC!Nestled in the charming community of Holly Ridge, this impeccable four-bedroom, three-bathroom residence epitomizes modern comfort and Southern charm. Boasting an open floor plan, split bedrooms, and a picturesque corner lot, this home offers the ideal blend of functionality and style for discerning homeowners.Spacious Layout: Step inside to discover an inviting open floor plan that seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The layout is designed for both intimate family gatherings and entertaining guests with ease.Private Retreats: With its split bedroom design, this home ensures privacy and comfort for all residents. The master suite serves as a tranquil oasis, complete with a luxurious ensuite bathroom and ample closet space.Versatile Living Spaces: Enjoy the flexibility of a one-and-a-half-story layout, offering a versatile bonus room that can serve as a home office, media room, or additional bedroom to suit your lifestyle needs.Outdoor Oasis: Embrace the beauty of outdoor living in the fenced backyard, perfect for hosting barbecues, gardening, or simply unwinding in the fresh air. The corner lot provides added space and privacy, creating a serene retreat for relaxation.Upgraded Features: This home has been meticulously maintained, with recent upgrades including new flooring, fresh paint, and a modern heat pump system(1 year). The kitchen showcases elegant granite countertops, complementing both the formal dining room and cozy breakfast nook. Water softener.Conveniently situated in Holly Ridge, residents enjoy easy access to pristine beaches, recreational amenities, and a vibrant coastal lifestyle. Explore nearby parks, golf courses, and waterways, or take a short drive to downtown Wilmington for dining, shopping, and cultural attractions.Experience the epitome of coastal living in this stunning Holly Ridge home.
